    <text>
        <body>
            <div frus:doc-dateTime-max="1950-06-10T23:00:00-05:00"
                frus:doc-dateTime-min="1950-06-10T23:00:00-05:00" n="50"
                subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d50">
                <note rend="inline" type="source">795B.00/6–1150: Telegram</note>
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">The Ambassador in Korea</hi> (<persName type="from">
                        <hi rend="italic">Muccio</hi>
                    </persName>) <hi rend="italic">to the <gloss type="to">Secretary of
                            State</gloss>
                    </hi>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <seg rendition="#left">
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">confidential</hi>
                    </seg>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Seoul</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1950-06-11T14:00:00+10:00"
                            >June 11, 1950—2 p. m.</date>
                    </dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>843. Re <gloss target="#t_Embtel1">Embtel</gloss> 842 to Department. Pyongyang
                    radio announced because failure emissaries deliver “Democratic Front” message
                    South Koreans owing firing <gloss target="#t_ROK1">ROK</gloss> forces yesterday,
                    Secretariat Central Committee Democratic Front directed same three emissaries
                    pass parallel 1000 today. Fragmentary reports police South Korea Yohyun village
                    these persons did come south, now being held custody. <gloss target="#t_ROK1"
                        >ROK</gloss>
                    <pb facs="0124" n="104" xml:id="pg_104"/> action uncertain, President out of
                    town; acting Prime Minister-Defense Minister and Home Minister will decide.
                    Initial reaction desirable shoot emissaries, subsequently considered bringing
                    Seoul, jailing; currently considering returning them across parallel.</p>
                <p>Department pass Moscow; sent Department 843, repeated info Moscow unnumbered.</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Muccio</hi>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
